óŔWarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2019-12-18-nushell-0_7_0.mdŔ@c2274bb2d49960231b8f38f7686978efa20f1ae8d800d7d8be6839578d2083a4ītitle: Nushell 0.7.0Ď¨What's next?ŕCYou might have noticed that with 0.7.0, we're seemingly getting close to 1.0. What happens after 0.9.0? Are we going to take the leap?
In short, not just yet. After 0.9.0, we'll release 0.10.0. Nu is maturing, but it isn't quite ready for the big One-Point-Oh. We'll continue maturing it until it's ready to make the move.
íźźŕ{Title: title: Nushell 0.7.0
Path: What's next?
Content:
You might have noticed that with 0.7.0, we're seemingly getting close to 1.0. What happens after 0.9.0? Are we going to take the leap?
In short, not just yet. After 0.9.0, we'll release 0.10.0. Nu is maturing, but it isn't quite ready for the big One-Point-Oh. We'll continue maturing it until it's ready to make the move.
